												<p>John Blair is an Emeritus Fellow of The Queen’s College, Oxford, and Emeritus Professor of Medieval History and Archaeology at the University of Oxford. His many books include <em>Building Anglo-Saxon England</em> (Princeton), <em>The Church in Anglo-Saxon Society</em>, and <em>The Anglo-Saxon Age: A Very Short Introduction</em>.</p>
